Subject Re Observation re helmets From Michael Seales In article , Norman Hamer writes Grf Dropped my Shoei RF off the seat of my bike while trying to rock it onto it's centerstand, chipped the heck out of the paint on it CONGRAULATIONS Your helmet just passed the Snell Test So I cheerfully spent on a bottle of testor's model paint and repainted the scratches and chips for minutes Oh well, as least it looks ok now Still, it may not save your head as well as before you dropped it Mike Mike Seales Yamaha XJ same as FJ Inform Group Ltd DoD Level DB Tower The Terrace Email Wellington Phone New Zealand Fax